## UVeye Career Page

# GitHub page:
https://toulouse6.github.io/uveye-careers/

# Live Webiste:
https://www.uveye.com/careers/

The UVeye Career Page is the official careers portal for UVeye, where prospective candidates can explore job opportunities and learn more about the company. The page is live and can be accessed at uveye.com/careers.

## Technologies Used
PHP
JavaScript
HTML
CSS
Comeet Widget: Integrated API

## Features

- Job Listings: Display current job openings with detailed descriptions.

- Responsive Design: Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices.

- Interactive Elements: User-friendly navigation and job application process.

- Company Insights: Information about UVeyeâ€™s culture, mission, and team.

